                                        ],
                                        "body": "The provisions of Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"#12\">12</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a> shall regulate the design, <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/14/heating-and-cooling-equipment-and-appliances#M1401.1\">installation</a>, maintenance, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/2/definitions#alteration\">alteration</a></span> and inspection of <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system\">mechanical systems</a> that are permanently installed and used to <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/2/definitions#control_limit\">control</a> environmental conditions within buildings. These chapters shall also regulate those <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system\">mechanical systems</a>, <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/W/3d-printed-building-construction#system_components\">system components</a>, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/2/definitions#equipment\">equipment</a></span> and <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/24/fuel-gas#appliance\">appliances</a></span> specifically addressed in this code.",
                                        "depth": 2,
