                                        "body": "In addition to the <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/Q/tiny-houses#AQ102.1\">general</a> administration <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/4/foundations#R401.2\">requirements</a> of <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/1/scope-and-administration#1\">Chapter 1</a>, the administrative provisions of this chapter shall also apply to the <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/45/private-swimming-pools#R4501.3\">mechanical requirements</a> of Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/13/general-mechanical-system-requirements#13\">13</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/florida/fl-residential-code-2023/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a>.",
